  "detailed_description": "Crimson Nights is a multiplayer dungeon crawler, where players try to survive floors of enemies. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayers can team up with friends locally or play for themselves in 1 to 4 player action! <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere are 4 game modes: <br />\r\n-A dungeon crawler game mode that players descend infinitely down different dungeons. <br />\r\n-A survival mode where players fight in one room against hordes of enemies. <br />\r\n-Player vs Player where people can fight each other to decide the best player. <br />\r\n-And a floors mode where an objective can be set for players to reach.",
  "about_the_game": "Crimson Nights is a multiplayer dungeon crawler, where players try to survive floors of enemies. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayers can team up with friends locally or play for themselves in 1 to 4 player action! <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere are 4 game modes: <br />\r\n-A dungeon crawler game mode that players descend infinitely down different dungeons. <br />\r\n-A survival mode where players fight in one room against hordes of enemies. <br />\r\n-Player vs Player where people can fight each other to decide the best player. <br />\r\n-And a floors mode where an objective can be set for players to reach.",
